th a \"Fing\" sound. \nThis is the only control in this game, you don't need a controller, just \"Fing\" the ground with your index finger, and you can clear all the stages of the game. \n\nYou can unlock 6 cute characters, and you can choose the main character for each stage. \nYou can play a total of 300 stages. when you clear the last stage, you can watch a concert of the 6 characters. \n\n\"FingFing\" is organized into four categories of games.\n Crossing the road, Find the maze, Block floor, Memorization\n\nImmerse yourself in a casual puzzle game filled with cute spaces and cute characters.  Master the art of finger movement and challenge yourself with increasingly complex levels. ", "short_description": "\"FingFing\" a VR healing puzzle game played entirely with your fingers"}]}, "developer_name": "AroundEffect Inc.", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://aroundeffect.blogspot.com/2021/07/aroundeffect-privacy-policy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "AroundEffect Inc.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://aroundeffect.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2691890164460465"}, {"id": "394813081514456"}, {"id": "377978390272490"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "6526112804179969"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 2, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "475775281997134"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "813159274241325"}]}, "b